text: Mya-Lecia Naylor (6 November 2002 â€“ 7 April 2019) was an English actress, model and singer. She was known for her roles as Fran in CBBC sitcom Millie Inbetween and Mya in CBBC series Almost Never. She also had roles in Absolutely Fabulous, Tati's Hotel and Cloud Atlas. Naylor was born in Warwickshire, West Midlands. She lived in London. Naylor hanged herself on 7 April 2019. She was taken to a Thornton Heath, London hospital while in cardiac arrest but later died. She was 16. Her death was announced by her agent A&J; Management on 17 April 2019. Naylor's death was ruled to be a death by misadventure.
